name: Charme villa
shortDescription: Holiday villa in the heart of Salento: a stone's throw from the sea! Discover the charm of Salento from this beautiful villa located just 50 meters from the crystal clear waters of the sea of Capilungo. With an outdoor space equipped with garden furniture, outdoor shower and barbecue, you can experience unforgettable moments outdoors.

name: Blue Home Catania
shortDescription: Blue Home Catania is an entire apartment dedicated to you and your family. Very comfortable and comfortable, with four beds in two separate rooms, it is ideal for your vacation in Catania. It is a short walk from the central Via Etnea and the metro station with which you can visit the whole city very easily.

name: Attico Magnificent
shortDescription: Get ready to be enthralled by the immense beauty of our stay, furnished with taste and attention to detail, where you will find the perfect place to relax and share special moments with your loved ones. A fully equipped open-space kitchen awaits you, ready to satisfy every culinary need and make your stay even more enjoyable.

name: Frejus Unit
shortDescription: Nice F2 of 50m2 with balcony and free parking space in a secure and green residence in Fréjus Plage.A real everything on foot that will allow you to enjoy the beach and local shops without taking the car. (Supermarket, pharmacy, bakery, tobacco press, bars.

name: A beautiful T2
shortDescription: We offer you a beautiful T2 equipped from scratch which is 200 meters from Calvi beach.Located in the heart of town in a quiet and farmhouse residence, with parking spaces. 100 meters from the main road of Calvi with many restaurants and terraces, 150 meters from SuperU and Weldom.

name: Apartment in the heart of the 20th
shortDescription: At the foot of the Campagne à Paris in a quiet and family neighborhood, you can reach the center of Paris in no time (less than 20 minutes from the Opera and the Marais by metro

name: Cergy - 1ch panoramic view apartment
shortDescription: Nestled on the 8th floor of a building, our apartment offers you an idyllic setting for an unforgettable stay in Cergy. With special attention to comfort and style, this modern space will seduce you from the moment you arrive.

name: Studio Hyper
shortDescription: Come and stay in  a comfortable studio of 15m2 located in Saint-Denis  a dynamic city on the outskirts of Paris.  Located in the heart of the pedestrian street, you will have all the amenities nearby.

name: Le Jungle & Cosy
shortDescription: This stunning apartment is fully equipped and perfectly furnished in a Scandinavian rustic style. Quiet and comfortable, it overlooks a quiet street with little traffic.Ideally located a 5-minute walk from the metro hoche, it will be perfect for couples alone or with a child, solo travelers and business travelers passing through Paris!

name: Samos Holiday Home
shortDescription: Charming first floor apartment, with panoramic views of island and walking distance to center of Karlovasi. Short drive to one of the most beautiful beaches of Samos, Potami Beach, and also the waterfalls. Sit and relax on the balcony watching mountains and the Aegean during sunset, and enjoy your holidays at this family oriented home.

name: Plous Apartment
shortDescription: Nestled in a quiet and traditional area, Plous Apartment enjoys an enviable location that easily combines tranquility with accessibility.

name: Bohemian
shortDescription: With its renovated concept in Gocek Gokceovacık, our villa is located in a peaceful location right in the middle of nature and green. Perfect for relaxing with a peaceful and calm environment.

name: Fethye Oludeniz Villa Aykurt
shortDescription: Forget your worries in this spacious and serene space.While you are enjoying sunbathing by our pool with a view of the Fethiye bay and sheltered, you will also enjoy your drink in front of this view.

name: Luxury Residence
shortDescription: Forget your worries in this spacious and serene space.Sit back and relax on this calm, stylish space.

name: Comfy
shortDescription: Admire the stunning architectural details of our charming townhouse, from the soaring ceilings to the intricate woodwork. Relax in our comfortable and well-appointed room, complete with modern amenities and a cozy atmosphere.

name: Stunning Single-level Knightsbridge
shortDescription: Nestled in the heart of London's prestigious Knightsbridge neighbourhood, this stunning Cadogan Square flat offers a luxurious and elegant retreat. Explore world-class shopping on nearby Sloane Street, indulge in fine dining at Michelin-starred restaurants.

name: Aspire Luxury Studio Apartment
shortDescription: Perfect for leisure or business trips to Birmingham, this cozy studio is close to major attractions and ideal for car travelers. Near Brindley Place and vibrant dining/shopping spots. Fully furnished with WiFi, Netflix, and a 50” Smart TV. Complimentary tea/coffee provided.

name: Luxury 2Bed Apartment
shortDescription: Cozy 2bed apartment offering a peaceful atmosphere making it the perfect home away from home. Langdon Park DLR Station is just a 2min walk away. From there, the journey to Canary Wharf takes around 5min, and the journey to Stratford takes about 7min.

name: Loiley Apartment
shortDescription: Just 10 mins to The 02 Arena and 3 Mins from Greenwich Station! This lovely apartment is spacious, clean, modern and bright. It features one double bedroom with one bathroom & a double sofa bed.

name: Hyggely Tisvilde
shortDescription: Welcome to our cozy and charming oasis in the heart of Tisvildeleje. Our cottage is the ideal place for your next vacation, whether on a romantic getaway or a family getaway.

name: Seafront Apartment
shortDescription: This self contained apartment is in the sought after Seafront location of Eastern Parade. Perfect for solo travellers, couples or families, looking to experience the charm of this beautiful place. Enjoy a comfortable stay with open-plan kitchen & stylish living area, bathroom, extra large bedroom, private courtyard garden, free TV & WIFI.

name: Seafront Apartment
shortDescription: Enjoy a stylish experience at this centrally-located place. Close to stratford train station for quick access to the city with westfield on your door step for shopping and the olympic park for a wander amongst the greenery!

name: Amber - Raffined Apartment
shortDescription: Amber - A stone's throw from the train station, discover the timeless elegance of this bright apartment with high ceilings and large windows, showcasing its beautiful marble fireplace.

name: Venice apartment
shortDescription: Enjoy a stylish and central home. On the top floor of a secure residence with east and south facing balcony for lunch on the terrace or lounge. Garage in the basement. Pool in the residence. Apartment completely renovated by an architect.

name: Cozy studio
shortDescription: This studio is conveniently located on the ground floor of a residence, just 5 minutes walk from the beautiful Calvi beach, as well as the city center and the port. The Super U is right next door.

name: Munich Garden Apartment
shortDescription: Stay at the peaceful apartment near Munich with garden and terrace. Close to the Messe München and with lots of possibilities to relax in the surroundings this stylish loft like stay is perfect for the whole family or for a business trip.

name: Sauna Apartment
shortDescription: Cozy holiday apartment with large balcony with private outdoor sauna, beautiful views and beautiful large bathroom to relax.

name: GERN Apartment
shortDescription: The far-facing view apartment is a residential dream with unique interior design, bright spaces, and stunning views. This is the perfect place to feel good.
